ges) and external risks (geopolitical headlines, macro auto-sector risks). There is no explicit bullish or bearish consensus in these pieces, but there is a cautious, observation-focused stance on Tesla’s autonomous-driving push and its regulatory trajectory, complemented by broader market context and cross-industry developments.']}
